<ul class="gcf-lyt-detail__tags-body sorting-list sorting-list--sdg">
<li><a href="/gcf/project/sdgs/1087" class="sorting-list__item"><img srcset="/gcf/images_cf/sdg/sdg_icon_8.png 1x, /gcf/images_cf/sdg/sdg_icon_8@2x.png 2x" src="/gcf/images_cf/sdg/sdg_icon_8.png" alt="SDGアイコン" decoding="async" />8.働きがいも経済成長も</a></li><li><a href="/gcf/project/sdgs/1090" class="sorting-list__item"><img srcset="/gcf/images_cf/sdg/sdg_icon_11.png 1x, /gcf/images_cf/sdg/sdg_icon_11@2x.png 2x" src="/gcf/images_cf/sdg/sdg_icon_11.png" alt="SDGアイコン" decoding="async" />11.住み続けられるまちづくりを</a></li>
